{
  "name": "Mission Control Daily Brief Emails",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 540,
        "height": 320,
        "content": "## Setup\n\n1. Import this workflow.\n2. In workflow settings, confirm timezone is `America/New_York`.\n3. Attach your SMTP credential to each `Send ... Email` node.\n4. Either set these n8n env vars or replace the placeholder expressions in the nodes:\n   - `MISSION_CONTROL_BASE_URL`\n   - `MISSION_CONTROL_ACTIONS_API_KEY` or `MISSION_CONTROL_API_KEY`\n   - `DAILY_BRIEF_TO_EMAIL`\n   - `DAILY_BRIEF_FROM_EMAIL`\n\nThis workflow only sends recommendation emails. It does not auto-apply `sync_today`."
      },
      "id": "9d1474b5-619a-4ddd-9d83-cd1d5325d76c",
      "name": "Setup Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -860,
        -520
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 540,
        "height": 220,
        "content": "## Timing\n\n- Morning: `08:05` ET weekdays\n- Midday: `12:30` ET weekdays\n- EOD: `16:45` ET weekdays\n\nMidday and EOD compute `since` as the same day at `08:05 ET` so the digest window lines up with the morning brief."
      },
      "id": "7d481e69-d436-4525-86a6-c3ed053a66c7",
      "name": "Timing Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -260,
        -520
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "5 8 * * 1-5"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "412064fa-35bf-40d4-be8a-d5272a783aeb",
      "name": "Morning Schedule",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        -860,
        -240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $env.MISSION_CONTROL_BASE_URL || 'https://mission-control-orpin-chi.vercel.app' }}/api/briefing/render",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "mode",
              "value": "morning"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "X-Mission-Control-Key",
              "value": "={{ $env.MISSION_CONTROL_ACTIONS_API_KEY || $env.MISSION_CONTROL_API_KEY || 'REPLACE_WITH_MACHINE_KEY' }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b4e89935-eefb-48f1-af6d-34ebd516ec53",
      "name": "Fetch Morning Brief",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        -620,
        -240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "={{ $env.DAILY_BRIEF_FROM_EMAIL || 'Baseline <change-me@example.com>' }}",
        "toEmail": "={{ $env.DAILY_BRIEF_TO_EMAIL || 'change-me@example.com' }}",
        "subject": "={{ $json.subject }}",
        "emailFormat": "both",
        "text": "={{ $json.text }}",
        "html": "={{ $json.html }}",
        "options": {
          "appendAttribution": false
        }
      },
      "id": "3c5f9b37-4f46-46ca-b876-32682525de06",
      "name": "Send Morning Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        -360,
        -240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "30 12 * * 1-5"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "819e4f74-1f7b-4584-81dc-2d8827ec695e",
      "name": "Midday Schedule",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        -860,
        20
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $env.MISSION_CONTROL_BASE_URL || 'https://mission-control-orpin-chi.vercel.app' }}/api/briefing/render",
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "mode",
              "value": "midday"
            },
            {
              "name": "since",
              "value": "={{ $now.setZone('America/New_York').startOf('day').plus({ hours: 8, minutes: 5 }).toUTC().toISO() }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "X-Mission-Control-Key",
              "value": "={{ $env.MISSION_CONTROL_ACTIONS_API_KEY || $env.MISSION_CONTROL_API_KEY || 'REPLACE_WITH_MACHINE_KEY' }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
